social_posts.post_text: Some Like It Hot and that ain’t bad!! 😜🔥 @somelikeithotmusical #broadway #shubert
We’ve officially opened @somelikeithotmusical on Broadway!! I will never forget this night! 🥹🔥❤️ Photos by the amazing @michaelah.jpg
Some behind-the-scenes from Opening Night! This cast has my whole heart. I’m so proud of what we’ve created together. I love you all beyond words. 🥹❤️🔥 @somelikeithotmusical

Steph, this still doesn’t feel real. Going through old videos of you made me simultaneously cry and smile so big. You used to make me belly laugh so hard with your sarcastic comments and sense of humor. You were the hardest worker I knew and kind to everyone no matter what. As a dancer, you were unparalleled. I was always so envious of how you had mastered every style. There will never be anyone like you. Thank you for touching my life during your time on this earth. We got to make our Broadway Debut together and be the Girls Who Eat Their Feelings! How fucking cool. I love you so much. I hope you’re up there dancing and choreographing away with Darius. Rest in Power, my friend. ❤️
Merry Christmas from our little family in our pj’s to yours. 🎄🎅🏼🌟 (Nikita didn’t LOVE her pj’s, but she was a good sport for the pic lol. 😸) #merrychristmas

Today we recorded the Original Broadway Cast Album of @somelikeithotmusical!!! 🔥 I can’t WAIT for the rest of the world to hear how delicious this one is. Mark your calendars for March 24th, HOTTIES!! 😜🎶🎤 #broadway #obc #castalbum #recordingstudio

It’s Tuesday which means it’s the start of our week over at @somelikeithotmusical and Pearl is “California Bound”! 🤩🎷🌴 Isn’t @gbarnesdesign a genius with these costumes? I will never get over it. 🥰 #somelikeithotmusical #broadway

A perfect Galentine’s excursion for 3 California girls who now call the Big Apple their home! 🍎🌇 I would’ve never expected having fun at a tourist attraction in the city, but this one was a BLAST. A super well-thought out museum ending with a fantastic ride where you fly over the city (very reminiscent of the old Sourin’ Over California ride at Disney!). I highly recommend it!! @risenyofficial

Still reeling over the fact that this happened! 😭 @mariahcarey, you are a true ICON and we were so blessed to have you at the show last night. Thank you for being a producer on SLIH and for believing in all of us. Come back ANY time! 🥹😍🌟 @somelikeithotmusical 📸: @michaelah.jpg
Happy Valentine’s Day to my loves. 🥰💕❤️
Jumping for joy cuz the fam is in town and seeing the show this week! 😍 Who else is stopping by?!

Beehive, anyone? 🐝 Had a spectacular evening singing 1960’s songs this past Monday at @classictheatremaryland’s monthly Cabaret with some fantastically talented humans. 🥰🎙️ #1960s #cabaret #beehive #classictheaterofmaryland

The @somelikeithotmusical cast album is officially OUT today and I can’t contain myself becauee it is HOT!!!! 🔥🔥 In celebration, here’s some behind-the-scenes moments of when we recorded one of my favorite songs, “He Lied When He Said Hello”. Which song is YOUR favorite?!! 😍🎙️🎶
Dushi Curaçao. 🥰🇨🇼🍹🌴☀️

Still reeling over finding out yesterday that “Some Like It Hot” is the most Tony-nominated musical of the season and that includes for Best Musical!! Congratulations to every single cast, crew, and creative team member! I couldn’t be prouder to be a part of this spectacular group of humans! 🥹🤩🎉✨🎭

SLIH Photo Dump #1. On Saturday, December 30th, 2023, we closed the most beautiful Broadway show, Some Like It Hot, at the historic Shubert Theater. It’s been a little over a week, and I’ve FINALLY gone through many pictures of this experience which brought back so many wonderful memories. Looking back at everything, my heart is incredibly full. I am so honored to have been a part of this project with these people, telling this story. We won 4 Tony Awards, recorded a cast album, performed on The Today Show, the Macy’s Thanksgiving Day Parade and others, and ALWAYS left audience members full of joy and love after every single performance. This was a special one and I will cherish it forever and ever. #HOTTIES for LIFE! 🥹🔥❤️ @somelikeithotmusical (Now please excuse the MANY SLIH photo dumps to come lol.)
